# for Cedrus) — a standalone package (core ffmpeg is 6.1.3, no v4l2-request, and
# its patches do not apply to 7.1). Stages libav* for the wfbvid player + the
# ffmpeg CLI for smoke tests; carries the prefer-linear-NV12 capture patch.
